Uses of Package
FESI.jslib

Packages that use FESI.jslib
FESI.Bsf   
FESI.Data Contains all native FESI objects. 
FESI.Interpreter Contains the interpreter itself (the xxxVisitor classes), then driver routines (Evaluator), the interactive interpreter (Interpret) and may utility classes. 
FESI.jslib Contains the public routines to access FESI objects and functions. 
FESI.Tests Contains a few classes used for the validation of FESI. 
 

Classes in FESI.jslib used by FESI.Bsf
